{"tid":334012,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"jobsxx點解咁多伏工落招聘","createTime":"2017-07-24T10:44:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T21:36:31.000Z","uid":73546,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a495e26486f0304e7b4f5428a1ae08906f208441","tid":334012,"uid":73546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T10:44:41.000Z","msg":"話說我每個星期都係jobsxx搵啲工send cv，利伸，俾呀媽哦到耳仔都甩咁滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一向都唔會掂有關Finance 呀，保險既公司。<br />\n直至我見到間所謂IPP financxxl advxxer 乜乜limited 請MT，唔知點解鬼掩眼send 左cv 。<br />\n岩岩就收到電話，叫我interview ，其實一切都好正常，直到佢講左句說話令我有點懷疑。<br />\n約好時間之後，佢話，咁我依加就pass俾人事部，如果你no show ，會black list你，可能會影響你係其他公司既interview 機會。<br />\n哇，收線之後諗諗下唔對路，梗係google下乜野大公司咁巴閉，你finance 公司黎乍喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一search 就見到啲人話其實又係sell客sell保險，又話大學intern界入面已經臭名遠播，blah blah blah。。。諗多陣 ，結果都係打番去推左，廢時俾佢black list我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1cb5669f7ca2a2841aeac260b9cbeea73de74e","tid":334012,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T10:46:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b30644ecfc9928738387f77c9425abc17214ff6","tid":334012,"uid":64576,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T10:49:31.000Z","msg":"一睇就知係保險"},{"pid":"ea851925d44a9cd5051b7f603e37d3244c7fb470","tid":334012,"uid":21423,"like":8,"dislike":24,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T10:52:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d34d33770594da21f21771bdbd1878daab13b396","tid":334012,"uid":69083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:13:56.000Z","msg":"已經唔會係JobsDB搵<br />\nAIA, Appco...都係大伏"},{"pid":"333f40a3374fe34eaf2d52329fec049f94b3f225","tid":334012,"uid":22889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:16:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已經唔會係JobsDB搵<br />\nAIA, Appco...都係大伏<